{"text_id":133618,"tokens":["Galaxy"," clusters",","," the"," largest"," structures"," in"," the"," Universe",","," are"," an"," invaluable"," probe"," of"," the"," early"," history"," of"," structure"," formation","."," While"," the"," mean"," relation"," between"," the"," velocity"," dispersion"," of"," member"," galaxies"," and"," their"," optical"," richness"," has"," been"," well"," studied",","," the"," scatter"," about"," this"," relation"," has"," been"," largely"," unexplored","."," Using"," a"," sample"," of"," ","2","9","7"," max","BC","G"," clusters",","," we"," quantify"," both"," the"," mean"," and"," the"," scatter"," of"," the"," velocity"," dispersion","-","rich","ness"," relation"," at"," fixed"," richness",","," and"," show"," that"," it"," evolves"," with"," redshift","."," We"," compare"," our"," measurements"," to"," predictions"," from"," $\\","Lambda","$","CDM"," models"," and"," find"," good"," agreement"," given"," the"," current"," level"," of"," statistical"," and"," systematic"," uncertainties"," in"," the"," mass","-","observable"," relations","."," We"," also"," measure"," the"," evolution"," of"," the"," mass","-","observable"," relation"," as"," a"," function"," of"," redshift",","," and"," find"," that"," while"," the"," mean"," evolution"," is"," consistent"," with"," no"," evolution",","," the"," mass"," and"," scatter"," of"," the"," relation"," at"," a"," fixed"," richness"," are"," consistent"," with"," being"," independent"," of"," redshift"," at"," $","z","<","1",".","2","$"," and"," having"," slightly"," more"," evolution"," at"," higher"," reds","hi","fts","."," We"," discuss"," possible"," systematic"," effects"," that"," may"," affect"," our"," results"," and"," the"," implications"," of"," our"," measurements"," for"," theories"," of"," structure"," growth","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"dolly","label":1}